        <p>
        If it is an element that is being dragged, then set the drag data store elements list to contain just the source node.
        Fire a DND event named dragstart at the source node.
        </p><p>
        If it is an element that is being dragged, then set the drag data store elements list to contain just the source node.
        Fire a DND event named dragstart at the source node.
